---
// Testimonial section
---

<section class="testimonial">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="testimonial-inner">
      <svg class="quote-mark" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
        <path d="M14.017 21v-7.391c0-5.704 3.731-9.57 8.983-10.609l.995 2.151c-2.432.917-3.995 3.638-3.995 5.849h4v10h-9.983zm-14.017 0v-7.391c0-5.704 3.748-9.57 9-10.609l.996 2.151c-2.433.917-3.996 3.638-3.996 5.849h3.983v10h-9.983z"/>
      </svg>
      <blockquote>
        "Sherpa finally made our playbooks feel personal. Wallet-aware panels, execution-ready quotes, and exports all show up without us wiring brittle frontends."
      </blockquote>
      <div class="testimonial-author">
        <div class="author-avatar">
          <span>HP</span>
        </div>
        <div class="author-info">
          <cite>Head of Product</cite>
          <span>Stealth Consumer Exchange</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .testimonial {
    padding: var(--section-spacing) var(--space-6);
    background: var(--bg-elevated);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
  }

  .testimonial-inner {
    max-width: 720px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .quote-mark {
    width: 48px;
    height: 48px;
    color: var(--accent);
    opacity: 0.3;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-6);
  }

  blockquote {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-2xl);
    font-weight: 500;
    line-height: var(--leading-relaxed);
    color: var(--text);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-8);
  }

  .testimonial-author {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: var(--space-4);
  }

  .author-avatar {
    width: 48px;
    height: 48px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    background: var(--accent-muted);
    color: var(--accent);
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    border-radius: var(--radius-full);
  }

  .author-info {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: flex-start;
    text-align: left;
  }

  .author-info cite {
    font-style: normal;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text);
    font-size: var(--text-base);
  }

  .author-info span {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .testimonial {
      padding: var(--section-spacing-mobile) var(--space-4);
    }

    blockquote {
      font-size: var(--text-xl);
    }
  }
</style>
